'''史蒂芬·夏普·尼尔森'''（'''Steven Sharp Nelson'''，{{bd|1977年|7月5日}}），[[美国|美国]][[大提琴|大提琴]]演奏家。为[[钢琴男孩儿|钢琴男孩儿]]乐团中最有名的'''大提琴男孩'''，经常跟随乐队去各地演出，其演奏视频亦在[[YouTube|YouTube]]大量发表<ref>[http://www.sacredcello.com/press.htm "Steven Sharp Nelson's Biography"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sacredcello.com/press.htm |date=20161101050615 }} ''sacredcello.com.'' Retrieved 10 January 2013.</ref>。

== 个人生活 ==
史蒂芬·夏普·尼尔森在7岁时，他的父亲决定让他的每一个孩子去学习演奏一种19世纪以前发明出来的乐器<ref name="wadley2006" />。史蒂芬·夏普·尼尔森最初学习小提琴，但他后来发现用大提琴演奏更有激情，于是转而学习大提琴<ref name="wadley2006" />。

2002年，尼尔森毕业于[[犹他大学|犹他大学]]，并取得了音乐学士学位。之后又获得了公共管理硕士学位<ref name="wadley2006" /><ref name="University of Utah">{{cite news|title=University of Utah Alumni Association awards $550,000 in scholarships and honors Piano Guys cellist and U professor|url=http://archive.unews.utah.edu/news_releases/university-of-utah-alumni-association-awards-550000-in-scholarships-and-honors-piano-guys-cellist-and-u-professor/|publisher=[[犹他大学|犹他大学]]|work=U News Center|date=April 6, 2015|accessdate=2016-12-26|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222105224/http://archive.unews.utah.edu/news_releases/university-of-utah-alumni-association-awards-550000-in-scholarships-and-honors-piano-guys-cellist-and-u-professor/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=U. to honor Piano Guys musician, professor|url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/865625851/U-to-honor-Piano-Guys-musician-professor.html?pg=all|work=[[犹他新闻|犹他新闻]]|date=April 6, 2015|accessdate=2016-12-26|archive-date=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810171644/http://www.deseretnews.com/article/865625851/U-to-honor-Piano-Guys-musician-professor.html?pg=all|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/705263044/Utah-pianist-cellist-working-together-to-make-beautiful-music.html?pg=all|title=Utah pianist, cellist working together to make beautiful music|date=16 November 2008|author=Carma Wadley|publisher=Deseret News|accessdate=10 June 2014|archive-date=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810210247/http://www.deseretnews.com/article/705263044/Utah-pianist-cellist-working-together-to-make-beautiful-music.html?pg=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在房地产企业工作一段时间后，他加入了[[钢琴男孩儿|钢琴男孩儿]]乐团<ref name="University of Utah"/>。

尼尔森相信他的父亲激发了他的音乐热情<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/865604593/What-fathers-know-best-Notable-personalities-on-what-they-learned-from-their-dads.html?pg=all|title=Father knows best: Notable personalities on what they learned from their dads|author=Lois M. Collins|publisher=Deseret News National Edition|date=8 June 2014|accessdate=10 June 2014|archive-date=2016-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113093119/http://www.deseretnews.com/article/865604593/What-fathers-know-best-Notable-personalities-on-what-they-learned-from-their-dads.html?pg=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他认为[[上帝|上帝]]促成了他的成功，但他不想把他的信仰通过他的音乐让其他人感受到压力<ref name="desert2013">{{cite news|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-35483041.html|publisher=Deseret News|location=Salt Lake City, UT|title=The Piano Guys: 4 Dads on a Mission|subscription=yes|via=HighBeam|date=16 December 2013|author=Bowler, Hillary|accessdate=10 June 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714131803/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-35483041.html|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-30801376.html|publisher=Deseret News|location=Salt Lake City|date=16 February 2012|title=The Piano Guys strive for a positive influence|subscription=yes|via=HighBeam|author=Hillary Bowler|accessdate=10 June 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714224007/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-30801376.html|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此外，尼尔森也是一个[[摩尔门教徒|摩尔门教徒]]。作为他的信仰的一部分，他曾参加了一个在[[韩国|韩国]]的[[传教士_(耶稣基督后期圣徒教会)|传教士任务]]<ref name="desert2013" />。

目前尼尔森的夫人是朱莉，并有4个孩子<ref name="wadley2006">{{cite web|title=Music is an escape, not a vocation, for cellist|url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/650196663/Music-is-an-escape-not-a-vocation-for-cellist.html?pg=all|date=8 October 2006|author=Carma Wadley|publisher=Deseret News|accessdate=10 June 2014|archive-date=2018-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123024419/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/650196663/Music-is-an-escape-not-a-vocation-for-cellist.html?pg=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 音乐生涯 ==
2006年，史蒂芬·夏普·尼尔森作为一个房地产开发商，描述他对音乐只是一种对生活的逃避而非一种职业，但他并未想到音乐反而在后来成了他的主要职业<ref name="wadley2006" />。后来，尼尔森签约了石头天使音乐唱片公司，这个唱片公司由[[保罗·卡达尔|保罗·卡达尔]]在1999年创立。

尼尔森在2006年发表了他的第一张个人专辑《[[神圣的大提琴|神圣的大提琴]]》，并入选了珍珠奖最佳古典器乐专辑<ref name="manila2010">{{cite web|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-219600539.html|publisher=Manila Bulletin|date=24 February 2010|title=A-List Performances at the Podium|subscription=yes|via=HighBeam|accessdate=10 June 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910231524/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-219600539.html|archive-date=2016-09-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="stoneage2014">{{cite web|url=http://www.stoneangelmusic.com/grace|title=The Piano Guys’ Steven Sharp Nelson releases independent cello collection with former record label.|date=6 March 2014|publisher=Stone Age Music|accessdate=10 June 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715001547/http://www.stoneangelmusic.com/grace|archivedate=2014年7月15日|df=}}</ref>，还进入了[[告示牌榜单|告示牌榜单]]前20名<ref name="manila2010" />。之后，尼尔森又在2008年发表了《[[温柔和慈悲|温柔和慈悲]]》专辑，在2010年发表了《[[圣诞大提琴|圣诞大提琴]]》专辑<ref name="stoneage2014" />。

2012年，史蒂芬·夏普·尼尔森和[[钢琴男孩儿|钢琴男孩儿]]乐团与[[索尼经典|索尼经典]]签约<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/865562412/TV-preview-the-Piano-Guys-enter-the-big-time-with-PBS-broadcast.html?pg=all|title=TV preview: the Piano Guys enter the big time with PBS broadcast|author=Blair Howell|publisher=Deseret News|date=15 September 2012|accessdate=10 June 2014|archive-date=2017-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170627134917/http://www.deseretnews.com/article/865562412/TV-preview-the-Piano-Guys-enter-the-big-time-with-PBS-broadcast.html?pg=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，他也和[[中国爱乐乐团|中国爱乐乐团]]有过合作演出<ref name="manila2010" />。

